---
const ITEMS = [
  { num: '01.', body: "Most AI demos are <em>dishonest</em>. They show the happy path with cherry-picked metrics. I won't put a number on a deck I can't defend in a one-on-one with the engineer who built the thing." },
  { num: '02.', body: "If a metric needs an asterisk, the <em>asterisk goes in the headline</em>, not the footnote. Hiding caveats is how teams lose trust fast." },
  { num: '03.', body: "I'd rather ship something <em>ugly on Tuesday</em> than something polished in six weeks. Polish comes after real users have touched it." },
  { num: '04.', body: "Boring industries are the best place to ship AI right now. <span class='terra'>Utilities, healthcare, gov</span>. Real users, real edge cases, fewer competitors playing dress-up." },
];
---
<section id="phil">
  <div class="w">
    <div class="cap"><b>Section 05</b> · Mind / mouth</div>
    <h2 class="phil-h reveal">Four things I'll <em>fight</em><br />you about.</h2>
    <div class="phil-list">
      {ITEMS.map((it) => (
        <div class="phil-item reveal">
          <div class="phil-num">{it.num}</div>
          <p class="phil-q" set:html={it.body} />
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  #phil {
    padding: 24vh 0 18vh;
    background: var(--cream);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .phil-h {
    font-size: clamp(40px, 6vw, 108px);
    line-height: 0.94;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    margin: 40px 0 80px;
    text-wrap: balance;
    max-width: 18ch;
  }
  .phil-list {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .phil-item {
    padding: 8vh 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
  }
  .phil-num {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: var(--terra);
    padding-top: 8px;
  }
  .phil-q {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(32px, 4.4vw, 72px);
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 96, 'wght' 300;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }
  .phil-q :global(em) {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--moss);
    font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 96, 'ital' 1, 'wght' 300;
  }
  .phil-q :global(.terra) {
    color: var(--terra);
    font-style: italic;
    font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 96, 'ital' 1, 'wght' 300;
  }
</style>
